data.description: Take your first step towards homeownership with this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home in Fern Creek!  Come home and relax in your spacious living room, cook delicious meals in the kitchen with newer stainless steel appliances, and serve your family and guests meals in the a large dining area. The huge primary bedroom has a convenient half-bath and good sized closet. Two more bedrooms and a full bathroom, complete with a gorgeous tiled shower, finish off the first floor. Downstairs you'll find the partially finished basement containing a family room area for fun and games, a multipurpose finished room, and lots of storage! Home has replacement windows throughout, new gutters with gutter guards, and the storage shed helps to keep the back yard tidy. Come see this home quickly
